data.description: This freshly renovated ranch boasts a fenced backyard, bordering wooded common ground for added privacy. Step into the inviting living room featuring gleaming hardwood flooring. Adjacent is the dining room, offering a charming window seat providing an excellent vantage point of the beautiful backyard. The dining area seamlessly flows into the kitchen, which has been tastefully updated with white cabinetry. The main floor master suite includes two large closets and a full bathroom for added convenience. Two additional bedrooms, each adorned with hardwood flooring, share another full bath. The basement is primed for finishing touches. An expanded carport provides ample storage space. With nearly 1300 sq ft on the main level, this home offers exceptional value. Conveniently situated in close proximity to highways, shopping centers, restaurants, and a variety of other amenities!
